headline: How To Earn $500 A Month From Paychex Stock Ahead Of Q1 Earnings
summary: Paychex, Inc. (NASDAQ: PAYX) will release earnings results for the first quarter before the opening bell on Tuesday, Sept. 30. headline: Jobs Data, Nike Earnings, PMIs: What to Watch This Week
summary: The Labor Department's monthly jobs report is due at the end of this week, but could be delayed if the federal government shuts down. Here's what to watch: Today   Earnings: Cruise line Carnival   Economic data: Pending home-sales data for August   Federal Reserve speakers: New York Fed President John Williams, Fed governor Christopher Waller   Geopolitics: President Trump plans to meet with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu.
